Simulation can be run with certain environment variables to cater to the PC running the simulation:

NumSpins => Number of spins to run
BetAmount => How much to bet on each spin
Threads => How many threads to run simulation on
DisplayGamePlay => Shows game play, displaying the reel result
DisplaySummary => At the end of the run, a summary will appear with additional stats
DisplayNumSpins => During processing, the number of spins spun and remaining will show